de.geofencing.client

Class GeofencingAdmin

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.geofencing.client.GeofencingClient
      • de.geofencing.client.GeofencingAdmin

  • public class GeofencingAdmin
extends GeofencingClient
    The GeofencingAdmin provides functions for maintaining the geofencing system and display the data. TODO Necessary permissions INTERNET, ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE BLUETOOTH, BLUETOOTH_ADMIN WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE
    Author:
    Markus Thral
